{"id": 3073, "genre": 1000, "title": "这年头你在线上都经历了哪些“小型困境”？", "description": "都不算什么大事儿，但放在一起，其实也算是当代生活的小小缩影了。（题图来自：iStock ©️ grivina）", "record_count": 5545, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191128010858k3PJqdsKNAh54mxR.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-27T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6070, "title": "这年头你在线上都经历了哪些“小型困境”？", "content": "这年头你在线上都经历过哪些“小型无奈”时刻？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349812, "content": "知道有些 app 可能侵犯自己隐私，但为了方便还是会装", "image": "img/option/option/20191127220756MfSkXDKaI3N2uY90.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349813, "content": "看社会新闻知道应该保持关注，但过几天还是会渐渐遗忘", "image": "img/option/option/20191127220850p3C0fqTDP8RoBcGd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349814, "content": "虽然明白阅读该有耐心，但信息一多还是会往短平快滑坡", "image": "img/option/option/20191127221133qO9MwP3hZsUK0QXL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349815, "content": "“手机解决不了无聊”的道理都懂，就是控制不住戳屏幕的手", "image": "img/option/option/20191128003555IvTiVkdfjbO389zH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349816, "content": "明明觉得社交媒体没啥可看，为了不落后于时代还是得刷", "image": "img/option/option/20191128002233TnMftClvxb9R3NhZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349817, "content": "尽管不怎么喜欢某些流行词，听久了也会不自觉地跟着用", "image": "img/option/option/2019112723094664PcOK2859DszFaV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349818, "content": "很清楚移动办公占用私人生活，但并没有勇气坚持离线权", "image": "img/option/option/2019112801113630VHxZAUEqrcBoMR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349820, "content": "知道应该多听不同的声音，然而最后还是缩回线上舒适区", "image": "img/option/option/20191128004726Wk7fQ9VSp0b1Jajo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349821, "content": "都没有/我有别的困扰", "image": "img/option/option/20191128011103Cruq8Dv7ePcGnwyt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}